Subject: Program unsupported error
Description:
Our scheduler suddenly did not sent an email for the weekly report. Upon checking, we noticed this log:

"The program is unsupported since: 2024-07-31 00:00:00Z)"

Please advise how can we fix this.

See below details for the current version we have:

Engine version: 3.0.0.0
Pro version: 3.0.0.2
Engine Compiled: 3/18/2023 8:26:23 AM
Solution_Comment__c:
Issue
Client was having an issue with their installation no longer being supported

Cause
They were running an older unsupported version of the product

Resolution
Client upgraded to the latest version of PC and the problem was resolved
